<BaseLayout
  title="Dog Walking Lake Mary FL | Professional Pet Walking Services in Lake Mary"
  description="Professional dog walking services in Lake Mary, FL. Serving Timacuan, Heathrow, Crystal Lake, and all Lake Mary neighborhoods. Bonded, insured, and trusted by local pet owners."
  keywords="dog walking Lake Mary FL, Lake Mary dog walker, pet walking Lake Mary, Timacuan dog walking, Heathrow dog walker, Crystal Lake pet services"
>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Dog Walking Lake Mary FL</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Professional, Reliable Dog Walking Services in Lake Mary's Best Neighborhoods</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <h2>Lake Mary's Trusted Dog Walking Professionals</h2>
          <p>At We Walk Dogs FL, we're proud to serve the Lake Mary community with professional dog walking services tailored to your pet's needs and your busy lifestyle.</p>

          <p>Dog walking in Lake Mary's beautiful neighborhoods like Timacuan, Heathrow, Crystal Lake, and Markham Woods means your furry friend gets to enjoy scenic routes, shaded paths, and safe, quiet streets perfect for exercise and exploration.</p>

          <p>Our bonded and insured dog walkers know Lake Mary inside and out—from the best walking trails to the most pet-friendly areas where your dog can safely stretch their legs and enjoy the Florida sunshine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-image">
          <p class="image-placeholder">[Image: Happy dog being walked in Lake Mary neighborhood]</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Neighborhoods Served -->
  <section class="neighborhoods-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Lake Mary Neighborhoods We Serve</h2>
      <div class="neighborhoods-grid">
        <div class="neighborhood-card">
          <h3>Timacuan</h3>
          <p>Beautiful gated community with wide sidewalks and scenic views perfect for daily walks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neighborhood-card">
          <h3>Heathrow</h3>
          <p>Upscale neighborhood with well-maintained paths and plenty of green space for your pup.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neighborhood-card">
          <h3>Crystal Lake</h3>
          <p>Peaceful lakefront community offering serene walking routes and fresh air.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neighborhood-card">
          <h3>Markham Woods</h3>
          <p>Tree-lined streets and quiet neighborhoods ideal for calm, relaxing walks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neighborhood-card">
          <h3>Lake Mary Centre</h3>
          <p>Central location with easy access to parks and walking paths.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neighborhood-card">
          <h3>Raintree</h3>
          <p>Family-friendly area with safe streets and sidewalks throughout.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Lake Mary Dog Walking Services</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Daily Dog Walks</h3>
          <p>30 or 45-minute walks scheduled around your routine—morning, midday, or evening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Potty Breaks</h3>
          <p>Quick 15-20 minute visits for puppies, senior dogs, or busy workdays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Exercise & Fitness Walks</h3>
          <p>Extended walks for high-energy breeds who need extra activity and stimulation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Puppy Walking</h3>
          <p>Gentle walks and leash training for young pups learning proper walking behavior.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Senior Dog Care</h3>
          <p>Slow-paced, gentle walks tailored to older dogs with mobility considerations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Large Breed Walking</h3>
          <p>Experienced handling for big dogs who need confident, professional walkers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Lake Mary Pet Owners Trust We Walk Dogs FL</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ Local Expertise</h3>
          <p>We know Lake Mary's neighborhoods, parks, and best walking routes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ Bonded & Insured</h3>
          <p>Fully licensed, bonded, and insured for your complete peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ Reliable & Punctual</h3>
          <p>We show up on time, every time, rain or shine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ Personalized Care</h3>
          <p>Every walk is tailored to your dog's age, breed, and energy level.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ Photo Updates</h3>
          <p>Receive photos and updates after each walk so you know your pup is happy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ GPS Tracking</h3>
          <p>Follow along in real-time and see exactly where your dog walked.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Map & Contact -->
  <section class="contact-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Visit Us or Call Today</h2>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="map-container">
          <h3>Our Service Area</h3>
