            <p>Serving Lake Mary, FL 32746</p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:352.682.5215">352.682.5215</a></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:jyl@wewalkdogsfl.com">jyl@wewalkdogsfl.com</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="hours">
            <h4>Service Hours</h4>
            <p>Monday - Friday: 7:00 AM - 7:00 PM</p>
            <p>Saturday: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
            <p>Sunday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Walk</a>
            <a href="tel:352.682.5215" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="testimonials-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Lake Mary Pet Owners Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-text">"We Walk Dogs FL has been walking our golden retriever in Timacuan for over a year. They're always on time and Max comes home tired and happy!"</p>
          <p class="testimonial-author">— Sarah M., Timacuan</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-text">"I work long hours and was worried about my puppy being alone. Their midday walks have been a lifesaver. Highly recommend!"</p>
          <p class="testimonial-author">— James P., Crystal Lake</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-text">"Professional, caring, and trustworthy. Our senior dog gets the gentle walks she needs and we get peace of mind."</p>
          <p class="testimonial-author">— Linda K., Markham Woods</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Give Your Dog the Best Walks in Lake Mary?</h2>
      <p>Join dozens of happy Lake Mary pet owners who trust We Walk Dogs FL with their furry family members.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Schedule Your First Walk</a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">View Pricing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

